con:interface.name: Event Engine
con:interface.con:description:
Event Engine is an aggregated, digitized bookings data that can be presented as event listings and can be delivered to custom segments across all platforms driving event discovery.
**Versions** v1 / v2 / v2.5
**Authentication** To run a successful v2.5 API call, you will need to pass your API Key in the request header.
**Example:** Authorization(key) Bearer `api_key` (value)
